Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:33.10,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲伤中寻觅自我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:49.23,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}在淡波间追寻儚梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:07.54,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}顿足向空深际蔚蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:18.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}包容渺小自我  继续向前迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:24.98,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}只望与你相见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.01,0:01:30.70,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}唯有以笑比心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:35.87,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}只因有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:40.81,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}心中充满光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:54.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}遥遥幽律逾破宙晓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:02:10.60,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}唯有醉情满溢心间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:33.10,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみに　試されるたび  少しずつ　強くなってく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:49.23,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}ありふれた　毎日の中　夢のつづき　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:07.54,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}歩きつかれて　見上げた空  深く　どこまでも　Blue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:18.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}ちっぽけな自分　抱きしめて  それでも　進んでく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:24.98,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}あなたに会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.01,0:01:30.70,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}笑顔を伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:35.87,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}あなたがいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:40.81,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}光が生まれるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:54.16,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}遥かなる　優しい調べ  遠い宇宙　越えて届くの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:02:10.60,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}胸の奥　かけがえのない  甘い痛み  満ちていく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,======================ED======================
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.11,0:24:06.98,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}黄昏に流れだした
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.16,0:24:10.68,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}制服の群れに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.51,0:24:15.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}逆らうよに　自転車の
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.96,0:24:20.13,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}ペダル　思いきり踏んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.42,0:24:24.79,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}放課後のグランドの脇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.85,0:24:28.27,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}金網をくぐって
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.33,0:24:33.68,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年　見つけた　ひまわりは
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.79,0:24:38.20,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年より　誇らしげに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.23,0:24:41.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}空を見上げてた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.46,0:24:47.00,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}折れないように　枯れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.02,0:24:50.79,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}涙に出来たなら
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.41,0:24:57.71,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}明日は何かが変わるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.39,0:25:04.79,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}雨降る日は　雨に揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.80,0:25:09.23,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}あの　ひまわりみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.40,0:25:13.46,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}まっすぐ　背を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.70,0:25:20.38,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}今日は揺れていたって、いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.11,0:24:06.98,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}黄昏下  逆行在流动的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.16,0:24:10.68,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}身着制服的人群中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.51,0:24:15.88,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}尽情地  蹬踩着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.96,0:24:20.13,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}自行车的脚踏板
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.42,0:24:24.79,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}放学后  操场边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.85,0:24:28.27,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}钻过铁丝网
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.33,0:24:33.68,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年发现的向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.79,0:24:38.20,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}比以往还要骄傲地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.23,0:24:41.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}仰望着天空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.46,0:24:47.00,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}不屈不挠  不会枯萎地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.02,0:24:50.79,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}若是放声哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.41,0:24:57.71,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}明天又会变得怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.39,0:25:04.79,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}下雨的日子  在雨中摇摆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.80,0:25:09.23,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}就像那朵向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.40,0:25:13.46,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}挺直了腰杆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.70,0:25:20.38,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}哪怕今日有所动摇  也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是大家都没有发觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:26.15,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1000)\pos(460,370)\fs29}第三类近距离接触
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽特派员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这40天辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…谢谢  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那么明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天暑假就结束了…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚  脚能够到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻血…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生病了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是姓？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野  加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌弃的话  我教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳的…方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不乐意的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我会拉着你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会痛的  要舔舔看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有电的味道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时间该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧  是认识的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  就像是那女孩兄长般的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个学校的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在这个时间还…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗是吗  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是暑假的最后一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也经常这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  对你这样的调皮孩子是很宽大的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C1  现在就出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C1  了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天是第一次游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真是多谢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  你先出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的人是不会伤害你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  浅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的整个暑假都和部长\N一起待在园原基地的后山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你一定没做作业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要完全照抄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点收起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也别对部长太过于唯命是从了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得多点作为新闻部员的自觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么  真的去找UFO了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍到照片了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  园原基地是UFO基地的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从很久以前就在流传了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是把隐形战斗机之类的给看错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里不就是航空自卫军和美空军的据点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照部长的原话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园原基地附近目击到的不明飞行物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是Area Sonohara的Foo Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}（Area Sonohara：园原基地；Foo Fighter：幽灵战斗机）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Foo Fighter？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:57.21,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}（紧急时刻  此路禁止通行）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是幽灵战斗机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是二次世界大战中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盟军飞行员目击到的不明飞行物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  当然  对于狂热爱好者来说\N这也就是UFO的别名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么认为呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最普遍的说法认为是\N园原基地在进行人造UFO发射
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收坠落的UFO后  模仿其技术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造出性能强大的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来  一旦发生战争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种UFO战斗机不就会咻咻地飞来飞去？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最多也就是演习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  防空避难演习？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那真的有意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像…这次演习的主题是真实性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(454,442)\fs24}Realism
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:09:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}啊  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}萌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}真让人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是伊里野 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是班长中{\fn方正黑体_GBK}込{\r}真纪子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不明白的地方都可以来找我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前住在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和哥哥两个人一起住的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人一起住在园原基地的居住区的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥是做什么的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  难道是飞行员？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英语一定很流利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.01,0:10:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有帮忙你哥哥的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}开学典礼马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}请全校学生到体育馆集合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}再重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}开学典礼马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}请全校学生到体育馆集合…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  浅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须藤同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和浅羽同学是认识的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  哪里遇见的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是亲戚？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  是以前的青梅竹马吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶穗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识那女孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  那她又为什么会那样盯着你看啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪里知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里遇见过？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是说清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:11:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  浅羽  你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸色刷白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  浅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.40,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs17}起因责任人  椎名真由美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好吃过早饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但现在好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班级和姓名呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年四班的浅羽直之
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年四的…浅羽？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧  你就是那个浅羽同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  原来如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开学典礼已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那位浅羽同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不舒服是吧  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有发烧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  有什么不对的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个吃了  稍微睡一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个暑假也许并不是那么糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对他使用了密斯特鸡尾酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(384,441)\fs20}Mist Cocktail
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种危险的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,植虫也应该用其他更好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你放进了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我认为这是个无可厚非的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在还不能断言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该是密斯特造成的幻觉重现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,441)\fs24}mist
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(454,441)\fs24}flashback
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  我现在只是一个保健老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密斯特的过量摄取
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我用红药水和喇叭商标来应付是不可能的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(254,440)\fs20}mist
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(374,440)\fs20}overdose
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联络不力的事情一定不要再发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an8}暑假结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an8}大家往往都会松懈下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an8}本次的防空避难演习
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an8}希望全员都要出席
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an8}以上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开学典礼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来的时候已经没人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上啊  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}啊  播报通知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}二年四班的伊里野加奈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}田中先生来电
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}请你速到办公室来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}再重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}二年四班的伊里野加奈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}田中先生来电
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}请你速到办公室来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我过去下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}以上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后可了不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中{\fn方正黑体_GBK}込{\r}她们都哭出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来转校生留着鼻血离开了座位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失口说错话了的话道歉不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可她却完全不认为自己有错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道她当自己是什么人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  吶  浅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天去社团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野特派员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽特派员和须藤特派员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疏忽了对如此优秀的人才的报告和劝诱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是太松懈了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「劝诱」是指…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们园原电波新闻部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是将有如太阳系般广大范畴的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以宛如电波般的速度提供给\N读者的少数精锐记者的团体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  特此欢迎伊里野特派员成为我部的新成员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…部长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  伊里野特派员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后再来拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  请代我向自卫军军官的令兄问好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  把花留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴似的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过时啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  这是部长你的提案啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:38.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月号的新企划
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「毕业纪念册里的显灵照」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还在拘泥这种事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天6月24日是世界UFO日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1947年6月24日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kenneth Arnold事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在华盛顿州的雷尼尔山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(396,441)\fs24}rainier
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了最初的UFO目击事件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的UFO之夏  开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电…电话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你在打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不方便插话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚…刚才  对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们的部长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在对园原基地进行取材
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是觉得如果拜托伊里野的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能够帮上什么忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  你哥哥是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是新闻部的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须藤晶穗你认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在部员还只有部长和晶穗还有我三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果伊里野也加入的话就有4个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比较忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  今天有演习
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防空避难…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急事态下的防爆姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是演习
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了因为是演习嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通行密码已变更
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(281,441)\fs24}route code
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔层的密码封锁完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和外界回路进行物理性隔绝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关…关上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}通行密码已变更
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的警报只是演习
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防空演习的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着  以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能会闯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是演习  不是战争啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争在1947年就已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是大家都没有发觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1947年…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kenneth Arnold事件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接通了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  浅羽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  是我  榎本
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…请问你找谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？什么嘛  昨天晚上在游泳池见过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我那时候没自报家门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这里也在想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你们还得在那里待上一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一阵算是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换伊里野？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来的确是演习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是空袭就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家全都死掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野的游戏机？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}mission Barrier Combat Air Patrol{\r}\N任务  阻拦式空中战斗巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以玩一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了  右边右边  向右散开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(472,441)\fs20}break
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反了  不是那边  反了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快了  就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了有了有了  B键  B键
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快按快按  FOX
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.03,0:21:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快按  快按快按
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  结束了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:21:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.47,0:21:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.27,0:22:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是伊里野吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榎本先生  喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野流鼻血了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在玩游戏  然后伊里野突然倒下一动不动了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身在抽搐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.06,0:22:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽  冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有意识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.01,0:22:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来  听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伊里野大腿内侧用力捏一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.74,0:22:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她有没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.14,0:22:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有动  没有动啊  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.98,0:22:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.81,0:22:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间紧迫  只能拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野携带的物品里有张灰色的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.25,0:22:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里找贴有「P-3KI」标签的箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.58,0:22:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.60,0:22:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它注射到伊里野的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.45,0:22:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱下内衣后就能看到胸口的标记
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.32,0:22:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口…？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.42,0:22:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是害羞的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.48,0:22:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到小学六年级都还和妹妹\N一起洗澡的是哪里的哪个家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会知道那件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻底成名人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.67,0:23:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.57,0:23:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.56,0:23:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.94,0:23:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫「什么啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.79,0:23:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西久保  花村
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.80,0:23:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电这东西  舔上去会有味道吗


